{"tid":1634683,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解嗌口號既人咁多 帶口罩既人咁少","createTime":"2019-10-07T09:25:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T14:45:13.000Z","uid":93540,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"16faf9d8b625a763de71b4b9bbc4d1cb4481b011","tid":1634683,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:25:39.000Z","msg":"口號既作用可以團結大家 激勵士氣<br />\n帶口罩都有佢既作用<br />\n就係話比人知蒙面法根本唔應該存在<br />\n係用黎話比全世界知我地唔怕呢個極權政府<br />\n香港人唔通真係怕左連口罩都唔敢帶？<br />\n全民口罩係得個講字？<br />\n你肯發聲嗌口號既同時 可唔可以帶上口罩<br />\n話比人知我地口罩底下 係我地既信念<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hgPqo4C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhgPqo4C.jpg&h=6e4e25d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UyHoaKE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUyHoaKE.png&h=4036f2b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1acde708ea70b3fba5ce993202b4089ec4a8ba84","tid":1634683,"uid":265192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:26:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10月<span style=\"color: teal;\">8</span>日：<span style=\"color: orange;\">提款日</span></span></strong><br />\n各大銀行總行撳錢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1634001\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1634001</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10月<span style=\"color: teal;\">9</span>日：<span style=\"color: orange;\">文宣日</span></span></strong><br />\n齊齊修補連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10月<span style=\"color: teal;\">10</span>日：<span style=\"color: orange;\">消費日</span></span></strong><br />\n全民幫襯黃色店鋪，18區排長龍<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1634353\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1634353</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JG49P0v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJG49P0v.jpg&h=bfdca82e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86f2914ccc8b57a4ce2ba199848348